H0.text: Dame Ninette de Valois, the eminent ballet teacher, director, and founder of The Royal Ballet and Birmingham Royal Ballet, was born in which country. England

A4.text: Dame Ninette de Valois was born in Ireland, then part of the United Kingdom.

A5.text: Ninette de Valois was born as Edris Stannus on 6 June 1898 at Baltyboys House in Ireland.
